 style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>maintained.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:3.1pt;margin-right:45.25pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:11.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n107%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Information security at Infopercept shall be driven by a\r\nwell-defined internal organization. Senior<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>management\r\nis committed to ensure that adequate security measures are being adopted<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>such<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span>that<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>the<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span>business<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>objectives<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.35pt\"> </span>are<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.35pt\"> </span>enabled.<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.3pt\"> </span>The<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>internal<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.4pt\"> </span>information<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.35pt\"> </span>security<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>organization<span style=\"letter-spacing:-2.95pt\"> </span>may seek support and advice from\r\nexternal parties like auditors, vendors whose controls<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt\"> </span>have been implemented in the organization and other well-known\r\nknowledge bases as<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>available.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:7.9pt;margin-right:45.4pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:11.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n107%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The Information Security Organization Policy defines\r\nappropriate responsibilities, authority<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>and\r\nrelationships to manage information security in all business units / functions.\r\nThe<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>information security organiza