(9, 'ISMS Management', 'ISMS Management', '2023-02-20', '0000-00-00', '<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin: 0cm 48.25pt 0.0001pt 11pt; line-height: 14.98px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The purpose of this policy is to establish an Information Security Management System<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\">&nbsp;</span>(ISMS) at ONLINE PSB LOANS and ensure management commitment towards information<span style=\"letter-spacing: -2.95pt;\">&nbsp;</span>security. The Information Security Management Forum (CSMSC) at ONLINE PSB LOANS<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\">&nbsp;</span>shall be responsible for ensuring periodic reviews of ISMS and improvements based on the<span style=\"letter-spacing: -2.95pt;\">&nbsp;</span>results<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>of<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.05pt;\">&nbsp;</span>the<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span>various<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>Audits<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\">&nbsp;</span>and<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span>Incidence<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.15pt;\">&nbsp;</span>Reporting.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin: 8.05pt 73.85pt 0.0001pt 11pt; line-height: 14.7px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The objectives of this policy and of implementing an information security management<span style=\"letter-spacing: -2.95pt;\">&nbsp;</span>system are:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 8.45pt 45.4pt 0.0001pt 47pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 14.84px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">To<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.55pt;\">&nbsp;</span>proactively<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.6pt;\">&nbsp;</span>identify<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span>the<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.55pt;\">&nbsp;</span>critical<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.55pt;\">&nbsp;</span>information<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span>assets<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span>from<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.65pt;\">&nbsp;</span>a<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.55pt;\">&nbsp;</span>client<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.65pt;\">&nbsp;</span>as<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.6pt;\">&nbsp;</span>well<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.55pt;\">&nbsp;</span>as<span style=\"letter-spacing: -2.95pt;\">&nbsp;</span>management<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\">&nbsp;</span>perspective.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0.15pt 45.35pt 0.0001pt 47pt; text-indent: -36pt; line-height: 14.7px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">To<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span>periodically<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span>assess<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">&nbsp;</span>the<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span>risk<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.35pt;\">&nbsp;</span>in<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">&nbsp;</span>order<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">&nbsp;</span>to<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.35pt;\">&nbsp;</span>ensure<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">&nbsp;</span>it<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">&nbsp;</span>is<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">&nbsp;</span>being<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span>adequately<span style=\"letter-s