(19, 'Roles and Responsibilities', 'Roles and Responsibilities', '2023-02-20', '0000-00-00', 'N/A', '<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:2.7pt;margin-right:45.2pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:11.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Security<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\"> </span>is<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.7pt\"> </span>the<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>responsibility<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\"> </span>of<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.55pt\"> </span>all<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\"> </span>users.<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.55pt\">\r\n</span>Anyone<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>with<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.6pt\"> </span>authorized<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.65pt\"> </span>access<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.65pt\"> </span>to<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.55pt\"> </span>Infopercept’s<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.6pt\"> </span>information<span style=\"letter-spacing:-2.95pt\"> </span>technology<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>resources,<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt\"> </span>including<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>permanent<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>and<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>temporary<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>employees<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\r\n</span>or<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>third-party<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>personnel<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\r\n</span>such<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>as<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n.05pt\"> </span>contractors,<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>consultants,<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>and<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>other<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>parties<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\r\n</span>with<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>valid<span style=\"letter-s